titles.title: Designating membership on certain standing committees of the House.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 2/4/1993--Introduced. Elects the following Representatives to the following House committees: (1) Dave Camp to Ways and Means; (2) Cass Ballenger to the District of Columbia; (3) Jennifer B. Dunn to House Administration; and (4) Richard W. Pombo to Merchant Marine and Fisheries.
